WEBVTT

35:37.160 --> 35:39.390 line:80%
I clearly pawned it as a redeemable pawn,

35:39.390 --> 35:41.430 line:80%
but I happened to run into
a dishonest shopkeeper

35:41.430 --> 35:43.870 line:80%
who sold it to
some dim-witted young gentleman.

35:43.870 --> 35:45.090 line:80%
That darn gentleman

35:45.120 --> 35:46.720 line:80%
actually paid 20 taels of silver for it!
